OL,6,FA Channel Islands car dealership has
OL,7,Fbeen fined #65,000 for unlawfully
OL,8,Fchanging the marketing preferences of
OL,9,Ftheir customers against their wishes.
OL,11,FA two-year investigation by the Office
OL,12,Fof the Data Protection Authority
OL,13,F(ODPA) revealed that sales staff at
OL,14,Fthe Guernsey Jacksons branch - now Van
OL,15,FMossel MotorMall - had been amending
OL,16,Fthe marketing preferences of some
OL,17,Fcustomers without consent.
