OL,7,Fbranch since the investigation began.
OL,9,FThe ODPA concluded these actions
OL,10,Fbreached two principles of the
OL,11,Fisland's Data Protection Law (2017),
OL,12,Frelating to:
OL,14,FThey further concluded these
OL,15,Fcontraventions were serious in scale
OL,16,Fbecause they were intentional.
