OL,6,FJacksons has been issued with a
OL,7,F#65,000 administrative fine and an
OL,8,Fenforcement order dictating they take
OL,9,Fcertain steps to comply with the Law
OL,10,Fgoing forward.
OL,12,FThe ODPA say the case serves as a
OL,13,F"clear reminder that transparency and
OL,14,Frespect for individuals' marketing
OL,15,Fpreference are paramount".
