OL,6,FGuernsey's Data Protection
OL,7,FCommissioner, Brent Homan, added:
OL,8,F"Respecting customer consent is a
OL,9,Ffundamental data protection
OL,10,Fobligation, which underscores the
OL,11,Fserious nature of this practice and
OL,12,Fsanction.
OL,14,F"Notwithstanding the serious nature of
OL,15,Fthis matter, I am encouraged by the
OL,16,Fcommitment of the new ownership and
OL,17,Fleadership of Jacksons to ensure that
OL,18,Fsuch practices do not recur and to
OL,19,Fprovide an elevated and exemplary
OL,20,Flevel of protection to its customers
OL,21,Fand their data rights."
