OL,6,FIn a statement, Van Mossel MotorMall
OL,7,Fsaid the company "accepts the
OL,8,FAuthority's findings and the fine
OL,9,Fimposed".
OL,11,FThey added: "The investigation
OL,12,Fconcerned the actions of a single
OL,13,Femployee, no longer with the business,
OL,14,Fwho, against established processes,
OL,15,Finstructed the change of customer
OL,16,Fcontact preferences.
OL,18,F"No further data protection issues
OL,19,Fwere found at MotorMall Guernsey or
OL,20,Felsewhere across our group.
