OL,6,F"As a Group, we take our customers'
OL,7,Fdata privacy very seriously; we are
OL,8,Fcommitted to ensuring that all
OL,9,Fcustomer communications are relevant,
OL,10,Fappropriate and proportionate to our
OL,11,Fclients' needs.
OL,13,F"We regret the historic failing that
OL,14,Foccurred prior to our ownership, but
OL,15,Fwe are reassured that the ODPA's
OL,16,Fexhaustive review has found no
OL,17,Fevidence of wider issues."
